divs: Sighting DetailsAbout 530 pm I was driving east on ave g near 50th west and Fox Airfield in Lancaster Ca. I was taking pictures of a weird cloud formation to the east and upon review of the picture I saw a black anomaly located in the upper right hand corner. The picture was captured while driving on a iPhone 5. The picture was taken through the windshield going about 70mph. I did not see the object. I really do not believe its a true UFO, and I think it's a possible camera anomaly and I am trying to debunk it first.
trends: There have been 15 other sightings in Lancaster

Summary: Found in picture that I took
